	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non eram dignus, ut vestrum aliquis Zofingę me conveniret<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Wegen plötzlich aufgebrochener Spannungen zwischen Zürich und <placeName ref="l2448" cert="high">den V Orten</placeName> war <persName ref="p1753" cert="high">Leo Jud</persName> nicht zum verabredeten Treffen erschienen, vgl. oben <ref target="file10607">Nr. 569</ref>, 1-8.</note>, qui non sine periculo valetudinarii corporis illuc redintegrandę amicicię gratia concesseram, nec ab eo tempore dignus fui vel a te unicum accipere iota.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si mea culpa id factum scirem, dolorem certe mihi gravissimum adferret, at cum mihi bene conscius sim de utroque vestrum, cogor tam absentiam quam silentium susque deque ferre et in angulo meo meos exanclare labores.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p5497" cert="high">Franciscus</persName><note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2"><persName ref="p5497" cert="high">Franz Kolb</persName>.</note> amplius prae ingenti struma<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a"><hi>in der Vorlage</hi> strunna.</note> officio fungi facile non potest, unde alio symmista indigebimus.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cuius gratia vestro consilio cum opus esset, non potui nec meum communicare nec a vobis exigere, nisi prius animo excident in universum, quod occasione neglecta votis meis erga te imprimis potin non potui.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernę</placeName>, ipso ascensionis die 35.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus Bert. H.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Heinrico Bullingero, fratri suo charissimo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
